Desert Wind (Boost) [Fire]
Level: Swordsage 7
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Six seconds

You convert your <i>ki</i> into fiery energy, allowing it to flow down your arms and across your weapon. For six seconds, your melee attacks deal an extra 3d6 points of fire damage + 1 point per initiator level.

This maneuver is a supernatural ability.
